title: New Caledonia Tourist Arrivals
description: Tourist Arrivals in New Caledonia decreased to 7816 in August from 8396 in July of 2022. Tourist Arrivals in New Caledonia averaged 8214.06  from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 15284  in December of 2019 and a record low of 61  in April of 2020. This page provides - New Caledonia Tourist Arrivals- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: ISEE, New Caledonia
